description: Seeks to provide current income that is exempt from regular federal income taxes by investing in municipal bonds that exhibit certain environmental, social and governance (“ESG”) characteristicsDesigned to invest in municipal bonds whose issuers are leaders in their sectors in delivering ESG outcomes or whose proceeds are used towards positive environmental or social projects ("thematic bonds")Actively managed by Nuveen, utilizing a value-oriented strategy designed to identify higher-yielding and undervalued municipal bonds meeting certain ESG characteristics
name: SPDR Nuveen Municipal Bond ESG ETF
